<% content_for :email_title do %>
 <%- if @order.gift? %>
              Thanks for purchasing a <%= @membership.membership_offer.name %> for <%= @order.recipient_name %>.
  <% else %>
    Thanks so much for becoming a member at Theater Wit.
  <% end %>
<% end %>
<%- if @order.gift? %>
    <p>
    Starting <%= @order.gift_date.to_s(:long) %>, <%= @order.gift_recipient %> will be able to to use
    member code <b><%= @membership.member_code %></b> to attend a wide variety of performances and
    productions here at Theater Wit.  If you'd like to get a physical membership card to give with your
    gift, just contact our box office at 773-975-8150; if not, <%= @order.recipient_name %> can pick
    up the card along with their first reservation.</p>
<% else %>
  <p>
  <%- if @membership.active? %>
    Your <%= @membership.membership_offer.name %> is ready to use immediately. You'll be getting a permanent card
    in the mail as well as a detailed brochure about how to use it?  But hey, why wait? You can start using your
    membership today.
  <%- else %>
    Your membership is not yet active. Sometimes it takes PayPal an hour to validate your subscription. In the meantime,
    we'll be happy to put tickets on hold for you.  Just call the box office with your name and member code.
  <%- end %>
  </p>
  <h4>
    Using your Membership
  </h4>
  <p align="center"><b>Your member code is <%= @membership.member_code %></b><p>

    <p>To use your membership online, just choose "Membership" instead of "Credit Card" as your payment method, and type
    in that code.  You can use your membership to reserve a single ticket to any regular performance here at Theater Wit.
    You can also drop by our box office with your code get pick up your tickets in advance in person if you're in the
    neighborhood.</p>
  <h4>
    Come as often as you like
  </h4>

  <p>
    Keep in mind that your membership cannot be shared with another person.  Until our box office gets to know you, please make sure to bring a picture ID when you come to pick up tickets.
  </p>
  <p>
    <%=raw @membership.membership_offer.email_html %>
  </p>
<% end %>
<p>
  Thank you for supporting Theater Wit and the many storefront theaters that make our home so special.  If you have any questions, please call us at 773-975-8150.
</p>
<p>
  See you at the theater!<br/>
  <%= image_tag "http://www.theaterwit.org/static/img/mail/jmwsignature.png" -%><br clear="all"/>
  Jeremy Wechsler<br/>
  Artistic Director,<br/>
  Theater Wit</br>
</p>
